                                    div.gl-paragraph Our partnership intercepts plastic before it enters the oceans and turns it into high-performance sportswear. We’ve only just begun.
                                    div.parley__content__button-container
                                        a(href="#" title="SHOP PARLEY" class="btn-text__black-theme") 
                                            span SHOP PARLEY
                                            img.arrow-icon( src="./img/Long_Arrow_Right_White.svg")
